        "title": "fix(telegram): consume trailing notify=false marker and send silent",
        "body": "## What Problem This Solves\n\nWhen agents append a trailing standalone `notify=false` to request silent delivery, the marker leaks into the visible Telegram message body. Telegram notifies the user normally despite the agent requesting silence.\n\n## Root Cause\n\nThe marker was not consumed before text entered Telegram delivery paths. Handling it in individual delivery paths (`sendMessage`, media fan-out, native reply) leaves gaps.\n\n## Fix\n\nConsume the marker once in `sendTelegramPayloadMessages` вЂ” the **shared upstream entry point** for ALL Telegram outbound delivery. One fix covers every path.\n\n- **1 file, 18 lines** (outbound-adapter.ts)\n- Strips trailing standalone `notify=false` from visible text\n- Sets `silent: true`, which maps to `disable_notification: true` in Telegram API\n- Inline mentions like \"use notify=false\" are preserved unchanged\n\nCloses #80569\n\n## Change Type\n\n- [x] Bug fix\n\n## Scope\n\n- [x] Telegram channel (outbound adapter)\n\n## Evidence\n\n### Full pipeline proof: marker в†’ silent в†’ API params\n\n```\nв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђ\n  #98150 Full Pipeline Proof вЂ” notify=false в†’ silent delivery\nв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђв•ђ\n\nв”Ђв”Ђ Phase 1: Marker parsing в”Ђв”Ђ\n  вњ… trailing standalone\n  вњ… marker only\n  вњ… whitespace tolerant\n  вњ… after blank line\n  вњ… inline (not consumed)\n  вњ… middle (not consumed)\n\nв”Ђв”Ђ Phase 2: silent flag propagation (all paths) в”Ђв”Ђ\n  вњ… text-only path: silent=true, text=\"hello\"\n  вњ… media caption path: silent=true, text=\"media caption\"\n  вњ… native reply path: silent=true, text=\"reply text\"\n  вњ… no marker в†’ no silent: silent=undefined, text=\"normal message\"\n  вњ… empty text: silent=undefined, text=\"\"\n\nв”Ђв”Ђ Phase 3: Telegram API parameter mapping в”Ђв”Ђ\n  silent=true  в†’ {\"disable_notification\":true} вњ…\n  silent=false в†’ {} вњ… (no param)\n  silent=undef в†’ {} вњ… (no param)\n\nвњ… ALL CHECKS PASSED\n```\n\n### Test suite вЂ” zero regression\n\n```\nnpx vitest run extensions/telegram/src/outbound-adapter.test.ts\n  Test Files  1 passed (1)     Tests  27 passed (27)\n\nnpx vitest run extensions/telegram/src/send.test.ts\n  Test Files  1 passed (1)     Tests  139 passed (139)\n```\n\n### Formatting\n\n```\npnpm exec oxfmt --check extensions/telegram/src/outbound-adapter.ts\n  All matched files use the correct format.\n```\n\n## Security Impact\n\n- New permissions? No\n- Secrets handling changed? No\n- New network calls? No",
